        "subject": "LU-6531 lnet: DLC interface for o2iblnd Channel Bonding",
        "message": "LU-6531 lnet: DLC interface for o2iblnd Channel Bonding\n\nThis patch migrates the Channel bonding interface to the DLC API.\no2ibs can be added, showed and checked via lnetctl, which uses\nliblnetconfig.\n\nThe original lctl and portals interface has been removed.  All future\nLNet/LND configuration should only be available via DLC.\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <amir.shehata@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I1d4710c42478e1dad800efb794313a834a77d2b2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
